{"article_id":"XfSMZjGAIOIGoncM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Syria 's foreign minister said Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that President Bashar Assad has accepted a Russian proposal","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to turn over control of Syria 's chemical weapons ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"potentially opening the door to defusing a stand-off with the United States","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as President Obama indicates","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"he 's willing to give the `` diplomatic track '' a try .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"According to the Associated Press ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Syrian Foreign Minister Walid al-Moallem said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"after meeting with the Russian Parliament speaker","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that his government 's officials quickly agreed to the Russian initiative","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to `` derail the U.S . aggression . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"At the same time , conventional weapons were still being used","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to pound Syria 's people ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"demonstrating","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that a settlement to the bloody civil war could still be a long way off .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"The AP released authenticated images on Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"showing smoke rising from buildings in a district of Damascus after heavy shelling .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The developments could nevertheless dramatically alter the nature of the national address","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Obama plans to give on Tuesday night .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"He had been planning to make the case for a military strike ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"but in the last 24 hours has eased off that call amid budding international negotiations .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid also postponed a test vote","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"originally teed up for Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"on whether to authorize the use of force .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Reid cited `` international discussions '' in his decision .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Russia 's Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov said","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that Russia is now working with Syria","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to prepare a detailed plan of action ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"which will be presented shortly .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"U.S. officials are approaching the proposal with guarded optimism .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"They cite concerns","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"about Syria and Russia stalling ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"and about the ability of the international community","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to verify the security of Syria 's chemical weapons .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Sen. John McCain , R-Ariz. , one of the biggest supporters of U.S. military action in Syria , told Sky News","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that the plan","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to have Syria turn over chemical weapons","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"is an `` option ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that should be pursued ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"though he 's skeptical .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"the `` first test '' would be for U.N. monitors to go to Syria","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"to secure the weapons .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Members of the Syrian opposition reportedly were skeptical of any Assad pledges","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to give up his chemical weapons stockpile .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"But Obama , in an interview with on Monday , opened the door to pursuing that option .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"`` We will pursue this diplomatic track , ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Obama told .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"`` I fervently hope","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that this can be resolved in a non-military way . ''","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"The president ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"while saying","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"his advisers would `` run to ground '' that proposal ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"indicated","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he still wants Congress to debate a resolution","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"to authorize a strike against Syria .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"it is important for us not to let the pedal off the metal","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"when it comes to making sure","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"they understand","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"we mean what we say , ''","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"But the president 's decision","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to pursue the diplomatic track","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"is a departure from his decision more than a week ago","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to pursue a military strike .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"And it could bring the temperature down a notch in the ongoing stand-off between his administration and the Assad government .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"The president 's comments come","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"after a proposal","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to have the Syrian government relinquish control of its stockpile","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"quickly caught fire in the international community and in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Secretary of State John Kerry touched off the discussion with an off-hand remark","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that Syria could only avert military action","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"if it turned over its weapons within a week .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Kerry and his aides afterward claimed","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the secretary was merely making a `` rhetorical '' point .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"But Russia 's foreign minister formally proposed the idea to Syria ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"and the Assad government said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"it welcomed the plan .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"As the United Nations secretary-general and several U.S. allies gravitated toward the proposal ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"the Obama administration conceded","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that it would seriously consider it .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` I welcome the possibility of the development , ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"`` We should explore and exhaust all avenues of diplomatic resolution to this . ''","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"the U.S. should be able to get a `` fairly rapid sense ''","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"of how serious the proposal is .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"`` We are going to be immediately talking to the Russians","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"and looking for some actual language","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"they might be proposing , ''","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"But Obama said","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"it 's important to `` keep the pressure on . ''","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Roughly quoting the late President Ronald Reagan ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"he said :","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"`` It 's not enough just to trust .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"we 're going to have to verify . ''","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"The president said","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"the idea","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"of negotiating this kind of solution","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"is `` something","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that is not new . ''","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"The president also brushed off comments","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"made earlier by Assad","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"in which he threatened","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"that there could be `` repercussions ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"if the U.S. attacks .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Assad 's military capabilities are `` not significant relative to the U.S. military , ''","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Obama said .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"The interview comes","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"as Obama prepares to address the nation from the White House on Tuesday night","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"-- as national polling shows","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Americans are increasingly opposed to U.S. military action in that country 's civil war .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"A new Poll shows","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that public disapproval of Obama 's handling of Syria has jumped from 40 percent to 60 percent .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"It also found","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"just 36 percent favor using force","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"to punish Syria","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"for using chemical weapons ;","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"61 percent oppose taking that step .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"`` Right now , the American people are not persuaded , ''","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"Obama acknowledged .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"`` Right now , members of Congress","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"who are just getting back","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"still have questions . ''","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"With the proposal so unpopular in the polls ,","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"Obama was having a difficult time","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"selling the idea of a strike to Congress .","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"A Senate test vote could still be held later this week ,","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"but the White House is struggling to corral the 60 votes","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"that likely will be necessary","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"to advance it .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"Senate Republican Leader Mitch McConnell was the latest","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"to come out against a strike on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"The administration faces an even tougher time in the Republican-controlled House .","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"Obama stressed in the interview","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"that the situation in Syria is `` difficult , ''","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"but the U.S. was looking at taking action","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"because chemical weapons","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"-- which the administration accuses the Assad regime of using --","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"are `` indiscriminate . ''","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"But he also said","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"he understands Americans ' skepticism over U.S. involvement .","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"`` The American people are right not to want to have us entangled in a sectarian civil war inside of Syria , ''","depth":5},{"id":146,"text":"he said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":257,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":163,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":157,"right":162,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":152,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":3,"right":150,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":6,"right":155,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":160,"right":161,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":158,"right":159,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":15,"right":16,"rel